Creating Colors for each cluster¶

In [35]:
def plotcolor(ar):
    cols = []
    for i in ar:
        if i==0:
            cols.append('red')
        elif i==1:
            cols.append('green')
        elif i==2:
            cols.append('blue')
        elif i==3:
            cols.append('yellow')
        elif i==4:
            cols.append('violet')
        else:
            cols.append('orange')
    return cols
